about:
   # Post-fader-insert-helper

   This post fader helper functionality requires post-fader-insert.lua script and JS: post-fader-fx-helper plugin. The script monitors channel volume faders, track volume and trim volume automation and sends the combinedvalue to the plugin. You need to have post-fader-insert.lua script running when using this plugin.

   Usage Instructions:
     - Run post-fader-insert.lua script
     - Insert JS: post-fader-fx-helper to a channel. You can now modulate other plugins with post-fader volume parameter.

   Dependencies:
     - None

